Fun little texture map, I made my self some time ago.

Originally aim_detective, but now also as a texture-map.

I made a bomb/defuse place and two spawns at each team to spice things up a bit.

Hope you guys like it, it is my first map (aim_detective really was, but this isnt that much different), so please don't kill me with bad response.
Do leave feedback though.

Hope you like it, I played it at my server som months ago, and know that some do.
